#. module: base
#: model:ir.module.module,description:base.module_pos_sale
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"This module adds a custom Sales Team for the Point of Sale. This enables you to view and manage your point of sale sales with more ease.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"\n"
