#. module: base
#: model_terms:res.company,appraisal_employee_feedback_template:base.main_company
msgid ""
"<em>\n"
"                Describe something that made you proud, a piece of work positive for\n"
"                the company.\n"
"            </em>"
msgstr ""
"<em>\n"
"                ອະທິບາຍບາງສິ່ງທີ່ເຮັດໃຫ້ທ່ານພູມໃຈ, ຜົນງານທີ່ເປັນບວກສຳລັບ\n"
"                ບໍລິສັດ.\n"
"            </em>"

#. module: base
#: model_terms:res.company,appraisal_employee_feedback_template:base.main_company
msgid ""
"<em>\n"
"                Did you face new difficulties? Did you confront yourself to new\n"
"                obstacles?\n"
"            </em>"
msgstr ""
"<em>\n"
"                ທ່ານໄດ້ພົບກັບຄວາມຫຍຸ້ງຍາກໃໝ່ໆບໍ່? ທ່ານໄດ້ປະເຊີນໜ້າກັບ\n"
"                ອຸປະສັກໃໝ່ໆບໍ່?\n"
"            </em>"

#. module: base
#: model_terms:res.company,appraisal_employee_feedback_template:base.main_company
msgid ""
"<em>\n"
"                Every job has strong points, what are, in your opinion, the tasks that\n"
"                you enjoy the most/the least?\n"
"            </em>"
msgstr ""
"<em>\n"
"                ທຸກໆວຽກລ້ວນແຕ່ມີຈຸດແຂງ, ໃນຄວາມຄິດເຫັນຂອງທ່ານ, ວຽກໃດທີ່ທ່ານ\n"
"                ມັກທີ່ສຸດ/ໜ້ອຍທີ່ສຸດ?\n"
"            </em>"

#. module: base
#: model_terms:res.company,appraisal_manager_feedback_template:base.main_company
msgid ""
"<em>\n"
"                From a manager point of view, how could you help the employee to\n"
"                overcome their weaknesses?\n"
"            </em>"
msgstr ""
"<em>\n"
"                ຈາກມຸມມອງຂອງຜູ້ຈັດການ, ທ່ານຈະຊ່ວຍພະນັກງານແນວໃດເພື່ອ\n"
"                ເອົາຊະນະຈຸດອ່ອນຂອງພວກເຂົາ?\n"
"            </em>"

#. module: base
#: model_terms:res.company,appraisal_employee_feedback_template:base.main_company
msgid ""
"<em>\n"
"                How can the company help you with your need and objectives in order\n"
"                for you to reach your goals and look for the best collaboration.\n"
"            </em>"
msgstr ""
"<em>\n"
"                ບໍລິສັດຈະຊ່ວຍທ່ານແນວໃດໃນຄວາມຕ້ອງການ ແລະ ເປົ້າໝາຍຂອງທ່ານ ເພື່ອ\n"
"                ໃຫ້ທ່ານບັນລຸເປົ້າໝາຍ ແລະ ຊອກຫາການຮ່ວມມືທີ່ດີທີ່ສຸດ.\n"
"            </em>"

#. module: base
#: model_terms:res.company,appraisal_manager_feedback_template:base.main_company
msgid ""
"<em>\n"
"                How do you see the employee in the future, do your vision follow the\n"
"                employee's desire?\n"
"            </em>"
msgstr ""
"<em>\n"
"                ທ່ານເບິ່ງເຫັນພະນັກງານຄົນນີ້ແນວໃດໃນອະນາຄົດ, ວິໄສທັດຂອງທ່ານກົງກັບ\n"
"                ຄວາມຕ້ອງການຂອງພະນັກງານບໍ່?\n"
"            </em>"

#. module: base
#: model_terms:res.company,appraisal_manager_feedback_template:base.main_company
msgid ""
"<em>\n"
"                Some achievements comforting you in their strengths to face job's\n"
"                issues.\n"
"            </em>"
msgstr ""
"<em>\n"
"                ຜົນສຳເລັດບາງຢ່າງທີ່ເຮັດໃຫ້ທ່ານໝັ້ນໃຈໃນຈຸດແຂງຂອງພວກເຂົາເພື່ອຮັບມືກັບ\n"
"                ບັນຫາຂອງວຽກ.\n"
"            </em>"

