"                first company at 30 years old and manage to grow Azure Interior\n"
"                from 1 to 55 employees mostly by reselling services on\n"
"                Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Nicole ເຮັດວຽກໃນຂະແໜງ IT <b>ມາເປັນເວລາ 20 ປີແລ້ວ</b>. ນາງ\n"
